channel.title: RSBot Update #524 - MagicTreeDrizzt
channel.description:
Hey guys, This is yet another RSBot script. [MagicTreeCutter]
[b]Features[/b]
[ul][li]100% Ent Detection[/li] [li]Starts in Cammy bank or at the mage trees.[/li] [li]Prone to Random events[/li] [li]Works up to 3 days untill you get banned[/li][/ul]
[b]Ways to avoid being banned[/b]
Make sure BreakHandler is on by opening client > Bot > Enable Anti-Randoms [Make sure box is checked. This is not recomended because Jagex are retards and they didn't detect my 3 day streak]
The Script can be downloaded by clicking [url=http://uppit.com/16BZS1]here[/url] [b]OR[/b] [url=http://rapidshare.com/files/173406436/MagicTreeDrizzt.java.html]here[/url]
Make sure you compile after adding the script into your script folder!
~ Java Is My Life™
